NOTES
========


The main function stores the value of overloaded value of ebp into ecx-0x4, it then loads the value of ecx-0x4 to esp which is i turn loaded to eip.
In order to load my shellcode to eip, my payload was 
<start of shellcode><start of shellcode><NOPSled><shellcode><Addrr of begining of payload+0x4>
